Package: rblimp
Type: Package
Title: Integration of Blimp Software into R
Version: 0.2.8
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Brian",
           family = "Keller",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "btkeller@missouri.edu")
Maintainer: Brian T. Keller <btkeller@missouri.edu>
Description:
    An R interface to run Blimp software for Bayesian latent variable modeling,
    missing data, and multiple imputation.
    Specifically, this package provides for generating Blimp syntax, running Blimp models,
    and reading output into R.
    This package requires downloading Blimp from <https://www.appliedmissingdata.com/blimp>
    in order to run the models.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    cli,
    methods,
    ggplot2
Suggests:
    mitml
